import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components';

const DivContaiter = styled.div``

const Widget = () => {
  return (
    <DivContaiter>
      <iframe
src="//www.facebook.com/plugins/like?href=http%3A%2F%2Fexample.com%2F&amp;kid_directed_site=true"
  scrolling="no"
  frameborder="0"
  style="border:none; overflow:hidden; width:340px; height:100%"
  allowTransparency="true">
</iframe>
    </DivContaiter>
  )
}

export default Widget
